- (Chuckles softly)

04:46.786 --> 04:48.038
- Bryce.
- Welcome.

04:48.121 --> 04:49.498
Welcome, Mr. Lorimer.

04:50.749 --> 04:53.543
- Hello. Felicity Lynn.
- Elsa: Hello. Good evening.

04:53.627 --> 04:55.547
