- Elsa: And Mr. George Diaz.

04:55.587 --> 04:57.347
- Mr. Diaz. Welcome.
- You gave my real name?

04:57.380 --> 04:58.441
Of course I gave them your real name.

04:58.465 --> 04:59.650
