- It's a pleasure to have you.

04:59.674 --> 05:00.735
Paparazzi? We're on an island.

05:00.759 --> 05:01.861
Of course I gave them your real name.

05:01.885 --> 05:02.969
Welcome to hawthorn.

05:03.053 --> 05:06.097
Mr. Ledford and miss westervelt?

05:07.349 --> 05:08.517
(Stutters) Oh, no. Um...

05:09.059 --> 05:10.339
Sorry, yeah, no. That was, uh...

05:10.977 --> 05:12.737
That's not miss...
