58:00.936 --> 58:02.229
(Richard groans)

58:02.312 --> 58:03.563
Anne: Richard.

58:08.276 --> 58:09.361
Slowik: Follow me.

58:10.195 --> 58:12.364
Into the tranquil night air.

58:20.247 --> 58:23.417
Don't be frightened.
